DataElement.preferredName: Protocol Agent Transfer Reuse Template Study Activity Repeat Duration ISO21090.PQ.TIME.v1.0
DataElement.preferredDefinition: An administrative activity defined at a global library level that is an action in which an authorized party at a designated study site dispenses or receives a study agent to/from a study subject, though as a defined activity, no actual study subject is identified. EXAMPLE(S): Dispensing a bottle of pills The period of time over which the activity is repeated.
